column4: just saying hello, that's all :) Do you want me to tell you a bit about the network?
Okay, it really needs some fixing up as you may see.
From me at cowserslauten, you get coal, ore, grain, and lumber
I noticed that when i checked the List of lines.
For my network to continue to function well, I need cotton from Carbon, and piece goods to go to the supermarket and cannery
For yellow and I, meat needs to move from cowser-knittern
wait is that   the name of citys or stops?
You exchange piece goods with Y Bahn at carbon
I am talking about the main freight interchange
With the exceptoion of that one through service and those two piece goods lines, you can remove the vast majority of the routes to construct

If you need help deleting public stations or building new ones without disrupting traffic flow, moblet and I have the public password and will be happy to assist.
Anyway, most of all just have fun ;)
I am leaving now, I am tired and still have stuff to do before bed. See you later.
